data.description: VA ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 3.2%! This charming 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is nestled in the picturesque town of Mulvane, offering a comfortable and spacious living environment. As a bi-level house, it boasts a unique design that provides both functionality and style. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a spacious kitchen that is not only well-equipped but also designed with a modern touch. The kitchen features an inviting eating bar, perfect for quick meals or entertaining guests. The adjacent dining area is flooded with natural light, making every meal a delightful experience. One of the notable features of this home is the lower level, which offers an expansive family room. This open and versatile space can be used for various purposes, from family gatherings to recreational activities. This home is located in a peaceful and welcoming neighborhood, ensuring a sense of security and community. With well-maintained streets and friendly neighbors, you'll feel right at home in this part of Mulvane. Schedule your showing today!
